Company Description: Founded IN 1948, Mcdonald's Operates As A Full-Service Restaurant. Based IN Northvale, N.J., Its Menu Consists Of Various Food Items, Including Burgers, Sandwiches, Chicken, Breakfast, Salads, Snacks And Sides, Beverages, Desserts And Shakes. Mcdonald's Mccafe Provides Mccafe Mocha, Mccafe Latte, Mccafe Cappuccino, Mccafe Hot Chocolate, Mccafe Iced Mocha And More. IN Addition, It Offers Happy Meals, Extra Value Meals, Dollar Menu And Mighty Kids Meals. Mcdonald's Also Provides Free WI-Fi, Arch Card, And Play Places And Parties.

Mcdonald S Is One Of The Leading Global Food Service Retailers With More Than 30,000 Local Restaurants That Serve Over 50 Million People IN Approximately 100 Countries Each Day. It Sells Hamburgers, Chicken, French Fries, Breakfasts, Salads, Fruit, Snack Wraps And Carrot Sticks. The Restaurant S Menu Features A Variety Of Burgers, Such As The Big Mac And Quarter Pounder, As Well As Chicken Mcnuggets And Egg Mcmuffins. Mcdonald S Also Offers An Array Of Beverages, Such As Soda, Ice Tea, Orange Juice, Milk And Coffee. It Also Features Interactive Game Zones That Are Designed For Children And Are Equipped With Stationary Bicycles Attached To Video Games, Basketball Hoops, Monkey Bars And Obstacle Courses. Mcdonald S Maintains A Location IN Brooklyn, N.Y.
